### 🎯 Module Goal

Is module ke end tak tum:

- Programming ko deeply samajh jaoge.
- Python kya hai aur kaise kaam karta hai samajh jaoge.
- VS Code setup kar loge.
- Python install kar loge.
- Apna first Python program likhoge.
- print() function use karna seekh jaoge.
- Comments aur basic syntax samajh jaoge.
- Errors ko pehchanna shuru kar doge.